data.description: Stunning 2 story home that offers tons of space from the inside out. Step inside the home with a modern feel throughout the home, with the many fixtures, colors and textiles all working together to create a welcoming place to call home. The living room is spacious with a stone fireplace, built in desk and large bay windows that allow for natural light to come in. The living room also open up to the exquisite chefs kitchen with blue and white cabinets, white granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. There is a breakfast nook that offers a large bay window overlooking the large back yard and patio deck out back, the formal dining room and office/study all downstairs. Make your way upstairs to see the spacious secondary bedrooms with a jack and jill full bathroom. There is also a large balcony for you to enjoy over looking the backyard and into the trees surrounding the property making it the perfect place to clear your mind and relax after a hard day. Appliances Included!
